msgid "Totem of Undying"
msgstr "不死圖騰"

msgid "Protects you from death while wielding it"
msgstr "拿在手就能保你不死"

msgid "A totem of undying is a rare artifact which may safe you from certain death."
msgstr "不死圖騰是一種罕見的神器，有時能幫你跨過死門關。"

msgid "The totem only works while you hold it in your hand. If you receive fatal damage, you are saved from death and you get a second chance with 1 HP. The totem is destroyed in the process, however."
msgstr ""
